node.text: 2022 Rivian R1T electric truck marries cross-linked adaptive dampers with air springs for world class ride, handling, and articulation. The Rivian's setup also shares the concept of using ride-height-adjustable air springs with several higher-end trucks and SUVs. But combining these elements gives the Rivian R1T several key advantages. Head over to our link in bio to get the full story. #rivian #R1T #motortrend
